Class AbstractTestMultiObsStorage<StorageType extends IObsStorageModule<?>>

  • java.lang.Object

  • Type Parameters:
    StorageType - type of storage under test

    public abstract class AbstractTestMultiObsStorage<StorageType extends IObsStorageModule<?>>
extends AbstractTestObsStorage<StorageType>

    Abstract base for testing implementations of IMultiSourceStorage. The storage needs to be correctly instianted by derived tests in a method tagged with '@Before'.
